title: Besides Lackey in Game 1, Matheny mum on rotation
text: > Top News Besides Lackey in Game 1, Matheny mum on rotation St. Louis Cardinals catcher Yadier Molina throws during baseball practice on Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, in St. Louis. Molina has been out since Sept. 20 with a partially torn ligament in his left thumb but expects to play while wearing a splint when the Cardinals faces either the Pittsburgh Pirates or the Chicago Cubs in Game 1 of the NLDS on Friday in St. Louis. (AP Photo/Jeff Roberson)
